## Pipeline Retro: openai-rust -- 7.9/10

**32 iterations across 8 runs, 9 plan tracks, 223 minutes**

### Top 3 Failure Patterns
1. **Deploy AskUserQuestion blocking** (CRITICAL, resolved) -- 7 wasted deploy iters from crate name conflict. Fixed mid-pipeline. Runs 3-8 zero-waste.
